{"tid":2499892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"13歲男童被捕　涉誘使三女童製作色情物品","createTime":"2021-04-22T08:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T09:22:25.000Z","uid":62632,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8d5460b5df6fb671b3325adb2b77c2f4661d56fa","tid":2499892,"uid":62632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:28:02.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警方拘捕一名13歲男童，涉嫌誘使三名女童製作色情物品。<br />\n<br />\n警方周三在觀塘拘捕一名13歲的男童，他涉嫌利用、促致或提供未滿18歲人士，以製作色情物品。<br />\n<br />\n受害人是三名年齡介乎9至12歲女童，去年透過網上遊戲認識該男童，男童以不同藉口，包括向三人提供遊戲的武器和裝備，誘使女童拍攝裸露照片或影片。<br />\n<br />\n警方初步調查後，相信這50多張照片未有轉載或出售予他人，不排除男童對性產生好奇而犯案，男童獲准保釋，不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\nsource：<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=432053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432053&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=fd29bd79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432053&h=5ca50dd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=432053</a>"},{"pid":"8612e25319daa290d748504f8d3d69e5b66946fc","tid":2499892,"uid":225192,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:06:29.000Z","msg":"大左做警察先犯法嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d0564a66277a722d0d677038a10d9653f5b905","tid":2499892,"uid":185935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:08:15.000Z","msg":"13歲有冇法律責任?"},{"pid":"59acb834bef7c478d8ca3e4646d3079bd1709282","tid":2499892,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:09:19.000Z","msg":"行前左<br />\n大個做狗 <br />\n姦完仲要求你唔好屈佢精神病 或國安佢家人"},{"pid":"5a6eaf258750b02fbbabf30a8e579015d05d0fb0","tid":2499892,"uid":49642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"13歲仔 依家Do靚仔咁早熟"},{"pid":"7a30a70101f6e25e159b717076929312f3559f3c","tid":2499892,"uid":365765,"lik